With blood dripping from her gritted teeth as she dragged the dead animal behind her, Suri Cruise reportedly deposited a mangled dog carcass on her mother’s doorstep Thursday and plaintively asked, “Suri get meat now?” “Suri share with Mommy, make present,” the 7-year-old said to her stunned mother, Katie Holmes, after lifting up the dead dog by the fur of its head and presenting it to her.